data.description: This adorable end unit ranch townhouse sparkles! The home has an open floor plan w/ the kitchen flowing into the dining area, flowing into the vaulted ceiling living room.    The white kitchen has plenty of counterspace, pantry and breakfast bar.  The spacious primary bedroom has a walk-in closet, 3/4 bath. There is a second bathroom, bedroom & laundry area on the main level.   This is a true beauty you will not want to wait to see! All information obtained from seller and public records.  Updated Roof and A/C.
